uliarity that in $J=5/2$ the state has zero width in the space of states\nchosen. All the states are bound with about 50 MeV with respect to the\ncorresponding $\\bar D B$ thresholds and the width, except for the $J=5/2$\nstate, is also of the same order of magnitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Apr 2013 10:34:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-18"}
