ications of the\nmodel are investigated for both the conservative and non-conservative cases,\nand several classes of analytical solutions are obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Apr 2013 07:20:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jun 2013 13:17:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2013 18:47:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-13"}
